title: Hi, need help with something.
body:
So i played a Yi game where i did some cool juke or something (i dont know) but it was 20 games ago. I click on full match history and find the game but cant download the game or anything like that. Is there anyway to be able to view a game i played 20+ games ago? thanks.
Game i'm talking about: https://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/OC1/193906879/201837210?tab=overview

replies.body:
If it's with Yi, it doesn't count.

FFS, 3rd time I EVER played him, I got a penta. He's just trash that should be eliminated from the game.
